name: How to woo(hoo) a god
description:
WARNING: This game contains copy written music and somewhat lewd images (NSFW).

press the qwer keys to serenade the gods and woo(hoo) them. 

You should check out the full soundtrack at: https://soundcloud.com/victor-blicher-buch/sets/how-to-woohoo-a-god-ost?si=ab114...
